===== Name
cljs.core/when

===== Type
macro

===== Signature
[test & body]

===== Description

Evaluates `test`. If logical true, evaluates `body` in an implicit `do`.

`when` is often used instead of `if` for conditions that do not have an "else".

===== Example

```
(when (even? (* 10 2))
  "10 multiples are even number")
```

